Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{user}}",
    "password": "{{password}}",
    "email": "{{user}}@bob.com"
}

###

POST {{MovieBase.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{user}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

